                "intervention_model_description": {
                    "_": "The exploratory RCT will inform us about the feasibility, safety, and delivery of the intervention; this will identify issues around its training, supervision and outcome measures.\r\nAfter the baseline assessment, eighty participants (N = 80) will be involved in the exploratory RCT (assigned to either the PM+ intervention (n=40) or the ETAU control condition (n=40)). The investigators intend to deliver the intervention to 40 participants, allowing us to test the feasibility and acceptability of the intervention in the proposed setting and inform the sample size for a future definitive trial."
